# Crew/flow agent status files — coordination scratch for the wave engine,
# useful for debugging a run but not a repo artifact. Plan files are kept.
# Pattern is agent*-status.md (no hyphen required) to also catch legacy
# agentN-status.md naming, not just agent-<role>-status.md.
**/docs/plans/agent*-status.md

# Fakoli scratch directory — run-time state, never a repo artifact.
.fakoli/

# Live fakoli-state store (never tracked in the marketplace repo)
.fakoli-state/
